{
"#useparam"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 x feishu 发送、监听飞书消息。"
,
"en"
:
"Send Feishu messages using x feishu."
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"飞书群机器人（x feishu bot）\n用途：向飞书群发送单向通知，无需认证，只需 webhook URL，仅支持发送消息\n常见场景：\n  - CI/CD 构建通知（GitHub Actions）\n  - 服务器监控告警（CPU、内存、磁盘使用率）\n获取方式: https://cn.x-cmd.com/mod/feishu/cookbook-1\n"
,
"en"
:
"Feishu Webhook Bot (x feishu bot send)\nUse case: One-way notifications to Feishu groups. No authentication needed, only webhook URL, send-only.\nCommon scenarios:\n  - CI/CD build notifications (GitHub Actions)\n  - Server monitoring alerts (CPU, memory, disk usage)\nSetup: https://cn.x-cmd.com/mod/feishu/cookbook-1\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"飞书智能机器人（x feishu abot）\n用途：用于发送和接收消息，通过指定模型启动后台监听消息服务，需要配置 app_id 和 app_secret（从飞书开放平台创建应用获取）\n配置命令：x feishu --cfg app_id=<id> app_secret=<secret>\n常见场景：\n  - 接入 x claw 作为私人 AI 助手\n创建指引: https://open.feishu.cn/document/develop-an-echo-bot/introduction\n"
,
"en"
:
"Feishu Intelligent Bot (x feishu abot)\nUse case: Full-featured bot with bidirectional messaging, can send AND receive/listen to messages.\nRequires: app_id and app_secret from Feishu Open Platform application creation.\nConfiguration command: x feishu --cfg app_id=<id> app_secret=<secret>\nCommon scenarios:\n  - Integrate with x claw as private AI assistant\nSetup: https://open.feishu.cn/document/develop-an-echo-bot/introduction\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"消息监听服务有两种模式（x feishu abot service）：\n1. --admin — 单聊模式（默认）\n    监听机器人创建者与机器人之间的消息，作为私人 AI 助手\n    首次启动需要配置 owner chat_id，服务名：x-feishu-admin-listener\n    配置命令：x feishu --cfg chatid=<chat_id>\n2. --group — 群聊模式\n    不指定 chat_id：自动获取所有群列表并监听每个群，服务名：x-feishu-group-listener\n    指定 chat_id：监听指定群，服务名：x-feishu-group-<chat_id>-listener\n"
,
"en"
:
"There are two listening modes:\n1. --admin — Private chat mode (default),\n   listens to private chats between the bot creator and the bot\n   First startup requires configuring owner chat_id, service name: x-feishu-admin-listener\n   Configuration command: x feishu --cfg chatid=<chat_id>\n2. --group — Group chat mode\n   Without chat_id: automatically fetches all group list and listens to each group, service name: x-feishu-group-listener\n   With chat_id: listens to the specified group, service name: x-feishu-group-<chat_id>-listener\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"chat_id 获取方式：聊天页面 -> 右上角设置 -> 底部获取\n"
,
"en"
:
"How to get chat_id: page -> Top right corner settings -> Bottom to find\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"飞书智能机器人接入 claw 作为私人 AI 助手：\n1. 配置 app_id 、app_secret 和 owner chat_id\n2. 启动飞书后台监听消息服务：x feishu abot service start\n3. 启动 x claw 接入飞书: x claw start --feishu\n"
,
"en"
:
"Integrate Feishu Intelligent Bot with claw as private AI assistant:\n1. Configure app_id, app_secret, and owner chat_id\n2. Start Feishu background listener service: x feishu abot service start\n3. Start x claw to integrate with Feishu: x claw start --feishu\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu init"
,
"cn"
:
"交互模式初始化配置"
,
"en"
:
"Initialize configuration in interactive mode"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu send --text \"x-cmd 新版本发布成功\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到飞书群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Feishu group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot send --text --chatid <chat_id> \"Hello\""
,
"cn"
:
"使用智能机器人发送文本消息"
,
"en"
:
"Send text messages using intelligent bot"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot service start"
,
"cn"
:
"启动智能机器人监听服务（单聊模式）"
,
"en"
:
"Start intelligent bot listener service (private chat mode)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot service start --group"
,
"cn"
:
"以群聊模式启动，监听所有群"
,
"en"
:
"Start in group chat mode, listen to all groups"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot service start --group <chat_id>"
,
"cn"
:
"以群聊模式启动，监听指定群的消息"
,
"en"
:
"Start in group chat mode, listen to messages in specified group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot service stop"
,
"cn"
:
"停止监听服务（单聊模式）"
,
"en"
:
"Stop listener service (private chat mode)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot service stop --group"
,
"cn"
:
"停止群聊模式监听服务"
,
"en"
:
"Stop group chat mode listener service"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot service restart"
,
"cn"
:
"重启监听服务（单聊模式）"
,
"en"
:
"Restart listener service (private chat mode)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot service status"
,
"cn"
:
"查看监听服务状态（单聊模式）"
,
"en"
:
"Check listener service status (private chat mode)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu abot service log <chat_id>"
,
"cn"
:
"查看指定会话的服务日志"
,
"en"
:
"View service logs for specified chat"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu react --runner repl"
,
"cn"
:
"启动交互式指令模式，将收到的消息作为命令执行并返回结果"
,
"en"
:
"Start interactive REPL mode, executing messages as commands and returning output"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:config"
:
[
"init"
,
"--cfg"
,
"--cur"
]
,
"send"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用飞书群机器人（webhook）发送消息（等同于 x feishu bot send）"
,
"en"
:
"Send messages using Feishu group bot (webhook) (equivalent to `x feishu bot send`)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu send --text \"x-cmd 新版本发布成功\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到飞书群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to Feishu group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu send --richtext   \\\n  --title \"Demo of Feishu\" \\\n  --text \"Welcome to x-cmd's website for details:\" \\\n  --url \"website\" \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\"\n"
,
"cn"
:
"发送一个标题为 \"Demo of Feishu\"，链接到 \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\" 的消息"
,
"en"
:
"A message with the title \"Demo of Feishu\" will be sent, linking to \"https://x-cmd.com/mod/feishu\""
}
]
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://feishu/data/send.jso"
}
,
