{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"管理智能机器人监听服务"
,
"en"
:
"Manage intelligent bot listener service"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"监听模式有两种：\n1. --admin — 单聊模式（默认），监听机器人创建者与机器人的单聊，作为私人 AI 助手\n   首次启动需要配置 owner chat_id，服务名：x-feishu-admin-listener\n   配置命令：x feishu --cfg chatid=<chat_id>\n2. --group — 群聊模式\n   不指定 chat_id：自动获取所有群列表并监听每个群，服务名：x-feishu-group-listener\n   指定 chat_id：监听指定群，服务名：x-feishu-group-<chat_id>-listener\n"
,
"en"
:
"There are two listening modes:\n1. --admin — Private chat mode (default), listens to private chats between the bot creator and the bot\n   First startup requires configuring owner chat_id, service name: x-feishu-admin-listener\n   Configuration command: x feishu --cfg chatid=<chat_id>\n2. --group — Group chat mode\n   Without chat_id: automatically fetches all group list and listens to each group, service name: x-feishu-group-listener\n   With chat_id: listens to the specified group, service name: x-feishu-group-<chat_id>-listener\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"chat_id 获取方式：聊天页面 -> 右上角设置 -> 底部获取\n"
,
"en"
:
"How to get chat_id: page -> Top right corner settings -> Bottom to find\n"
}
]
