}
]
}
}
,
"listen"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"长轮询监听飞书消息"
,
"en"
:
"Long-polling listener for Feishu messages"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"监听模式有两种：\n1. --admin — 单聊模式（默认），监听机器人创建者与机器人之间的单聊\n2. --group — 群聊模式，不指定 chat_id 则自动获取所有群列表并监听每个群\n"
,
"en"
:
"There are two listening modes:\n1. --admin — Private chat mode (default), listens to private chats between the bot creator and the bot\n2. --group — Group chat mode, automatically fetches all group list and listens to each group if chat_id not provided\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"输出方式有两种：\n1. --fp — 将接收到的消息保存到数据文件（默认路径 ~/.x-cmd-feishu/data_<chat_id>.tsv）\n2. --json — 以 JSON 格式输出消息到标准输出\n"
,
"en"
:
"There are two output modes:\n1. --fp — Save received messages to data file (default path ~/.x-cmd-feishu/data_<chat_id>.tsv)\n2. --json — Output messages in JSON format to stdout\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu listen"
,
"cn"
:
"启动长轮询监听飞书消息（单聊模式）"
,
"en"
:
"Start long-polling listener for Feishu messages (private chat mode)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu listen --admin"
,
"cn"
:
"以单聊模式监听"
,
"en"
:
"Listen in private chat mode"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu listen --group"
,
"cn"
:
"以群聊模式监听所有群的消息"
,
"en"
:
"Listen in group chat mode for all group messages"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu listen --group <chat_id>"
,
"cn"
:
"以群聊模式监听指定群的消息"
,
"en"
:
"Listen in group chat mode for messages in specified group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu listen --fp"
,
"cn"
:
"启动监听并保存消息到数据文件"
,
"en"
:
"Start listener and save messages to data file"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu listen --json"
,
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出消息"
,
"en"
:
"Output messages in JSON format"
}
]
,
"--admin"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以单聊模式监听"
,
"en"
:
"Listen in private chat mode"
}
}
,
"--group"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以群聊模式监听，不提供 chat_id 则自动获取所有群列表并监听每个群"
,
"en"
:
"Listen in group chat mode, automatically fetches all group list if chat_id not provided"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"群 chat_id（可选，不提供则监听所有群聊）"
,
"en"
:
"Group chat_id (optional, listens to all groups if not provided)"
}
}
}
,
"--fp"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"将接收到的消息保存到数据文件"
,
"en"
:
"Save received messages to data file"
}
}
,
"--json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出消息"
,
