,
"login"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Login to create a Feishu bot via QR code scan"
,
"cn"
:
"扫描二维码登录创建飞书机器人"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"飞书机器人登录（x feishu login）\n用途：通过扫描飞书 App 中的二维码，创建并配置智能机器人\n该命令会获取 app_id 和 app_secret 并自动保存到配置\n登录成功后可直接使用智能机器人功能\n"
,
"en"
:
"Feishu Bot Login (x feishu login)\nUse case: Create a Feishu intelligent bot by scanning a QR code with the Feishu App\nThis command retrieves app_id and app_secret and automatically saves them to the config\nAfter successful login, you can directly use the intelligent bot features\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x feishu login"
,
"cn"
:
"扫描二维码登录创建飞书机器人"
,
"en"
:
"Scan QR code to login and create Feishu bot"
}
]
}
,
